Whether the path variable is required._

Defaults to {@code true}, leading to an exception being thrown if the path_variable is missing in the incoming request. Switch this to {@code false} if_you prefer a {@code null} or Java 8 {@code java.util.Optional} in this case._e.g. on a {@code ModelAttribute} method which serves for different requests._@since 4.3.3
